92
00:10:20,004 --> 00:10:24,008
I'm losing hair where I want hair,
and getting one where it shouldn't be hair.

93
00:10:24,008 --> 00:10:27,720
I found four big fat ones on my back.
I'm starting to look like the fly.

94
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:30,806
That's it. I'm cancelling
your birthday party.

95
00:10:32,057 --> 00:10:34,893
- Why?
- Cos your birthdays depress you.

96
00:10:34,977 --> 00:10:36,979
- No, they don't.
- Oh, Mitch.

97
00:10:36,979 --> 00:10:39,982
On your 30th birthday,
you said you couldn't see.

98
00:10:39,982 --> 00:10:43,402
On your 34th birthday,
you forgot my name for an hour.

99
00:10:43,485 --> 00:10:46,655
Last year, when I asked you
what you wanted...

100
00:10:46,655 --> 00:10:48,699
...you said a CAT scan.

101
00:10:49,158 --> 00:10:52,661
- I had a headache.
- This year, let's just let it pass.

102
00:10:53,203 --> 00:10:55,873
- I wanna see my friends.
- All right.

103
00:10:55,873 --> 00:10:59,877
But I don't want people coming over here
thinking they're in a Bergman film.

104
00:10:59,877 --> 00:11:02,504
"You've met my husband, Mr Death?"

105
00:11:03,505 --> 00:11:05,591
- I'll be good.
- Yeah?

106
00:11:05,591 --> 00:11:08,761
Cos I don't need you
any worse than you've been.

107
00:11:10,262 --> 00:11:13,432
- Wait a second. What does that mean?
- Nothing.

108
00:11:13,766 --> 00:11:15,392
"Nothing."

109
00:11:15,768 --> 00:11:17,144
Great.

110
