- I see your point.

766
01:01:27,863 --> 01:01:29,865
Come on.
She's ready.

767
01:01:32,076 --> 01:01:34,036
- I...
- She's burstin'!

768
01:01:34,036 --> 01:01:36,455
Oh, God.
There's gonna be bursting?

769
01:01:36,455 --> 01:01:39,083
Just reach in and pull out the calf.

770
