Ooh.

771
01:02:00,813 --> 01:02:04,942
- You know, this was not in the brochure.
- She needs help, goddamn it!

772
01:02:09,780 --> 01:02:12,741
What's taking so long?
Do you see the head?

773
01:02:15,452 --> 01:02:16,453
