774
01:02:20,457 --> 01:02:22,960
- I only see a tail.
- Oh, shit.

775
01:02:23,210 --> 01:02:25,921
It's turned the wrong way.
Get it out.

776
01:02:27,631 --> 01:02:29,008
Uh-oh.

777
01:02:29,133 --> 01:02:30,968
- My watch came off.
- Now!

778
01:02:30,968 --> 01:02:33,178
- It was a gift!
- Do it!

779
01:02:35,973 --> 01:02:37,433
