Curly?

858
01:08:42,298 --> 01:08:46,719
Is this all right? Do you need, like, a
licence or something to bury somebody?

859
01:08:47,219 --> 01:08:50,055
Nah. This is where
Curly'd wanna be buried.

860
01:08:50,055 --> 01:08:53,600
He said he was a dying breed.
I didn't know he meant on this trip.

861
01:08:53,600 --> 01:08:57,229
The man ate bacon at every meal.
I mean, you can't do that.

862
01:08:57,896 --> 01:09:00,024
Well, I guess that's it.

863
01:09:00,107 --> 01:09:03,902
Wait a minute. Shouldn't somebody
say something? Like a eulogy.

864
01:09:04,111 --> 01:09:06,780
- Yeah.
- Cookie, you knew him best.

865
01:09:12,536 --> 01:09:16,999
Lord, we give you Curly.
Try not to piss him off.

866
01:09:17,791 --> 01:09:19,335
That's it?

867
01:09:19,627 --> 01:09:22,046
What else is there?
I got chicken burning.

868
01:09:22,046 --> 01:09:25,257
You're a warm man, Cookie.
Wait a second. I'll...

869
01:09:29,470 --> 01:09:31,722
What can I say about Curly?

870
